  • Classes in maven.websphere.plugin used by maven.websphere.plugin 
    Class and Description
    AbstractExportMojo
    Super class of all the export mojos, defines the output file to be executed.
    AbstractMigrateMojo
    Super class of migrate mojo's, defines migration work flow for pages,portlet, theme and urlmappings.
    AbstractMultiDeployMojo 
    AbstractWebsphereMojo
    Accommodate MAVEN attribute, and common method which needs MAVEN attributes
    AbstractWSAntMojo 
    AbstractXMLAccessMojo
    Super class of XMLAccess related goals, define the work follow of XMLAccess execution
    DeployEARMojo
    The deploy-ear task enables you to install a new application into a WebSphere Server or Cell.This task is a wrapper for the AdminApp.install() command of the wsadmin tool.
    DeployMojoIface 
    DeployPortletMojo
    The deploy-portlet task enables you to install portlet into a WebSphere Portal Server.
    ExportPageMojo
    The export-page task enables you to export the WebSphere Portal Page based on UniqueName.
    ExportPortletMojo
    The export-portlet task enables you to export the WebSphere portlet(s) based on UniqueName(s).
    ExportThemeMojo
    The export-theme task enables you to export the WebSphere Theme based on Theme.
    ExportURLMappingMojo
    The export-urlmapping task enables you to export the WebSphere urlmapping based on Uniquename or label.
